   <p begin="00:16:53.722" end="00:16:57.267" style="s1"><span style="s2">ピカ… チュー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:16:57.892" end="00:16:59.352" style="s1"><span style="s2">ちょっと 大丈夫なの？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:16:59.436" end="00:17:02.480" style="s1"><span style="s2">大丈夫<br />科学に不可能はありません</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:17:02.564" end="00:17:03.773" style="s1"><span style="s2">頑張れ ピカチュウ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:17:03.857" end="00:17:07.193" style="s1"><span style="s2">チュー！　ピッカ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:17:07.277" end="00:17:09.821" style="s1"><span style="s2">（セレナ）キャー<br />（サトシ）うわあっ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:17:15.618" end="00:17:17.829" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ピカチュウ）ピカ？<br />（シトロン）ああ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:17:17.912" end="00:17:20.915" style="s1"><span style="s2">（セレナ）やっぱりダメ…<br />（ユリーカ）また失敗だね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:17:20.999" end="00:17:24.419" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ピチュー）ピチュー？<br />（シトロン）途中までは完璧だったんです</span></p> 
