   <p begin="00:17:28.089" end="00:17:30.175" style="s1"><span style="s2">（セレナ）そうね<br />（レナ）ピチュー？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:17:30.258" end="00:17:33.011" style="s1"><span style="s2">（一同）ん？<br />（ピチュー）ピチュー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:17:34.471" end="00:17:37.474" style="s1"><span style="s2">ピチュー　よかった</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:17:39.392" end="00:17:41.019" style="s1"><span style="s2">（レナ）リムはどこ？<br />（ピチュー）ピチュー？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:17:41.102" end="00:17:42.645" style="s1"><span style="s2">（シトロン）もしかして…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:17:43.646" end="00:17:45.690" style="s1"><span style="s2">（レナ）あなたたちは<br />ポケモンセンターで…</span></p> 
