   <p begin="00:17:48.985" end="00:17:51.613" style="s1"><span style="s2">（レナ）ええ そうよ　私はレナ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:17:51.696" end="00:17:53.823" style="s1"><span style="s2">あなたたちが<br />この子を見つけてくれたの？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:17:54.324" end="00:17:56.242" style="s1"><span style="s2">見つけたというか…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:17:56.326" end="00:17:58.453" style="s1"><span style="s2">デデンネ　デデンネはどこ？</span></p> 
