   <p begin="00:19:25.790" end="00:19:27.417" style="s1"><span style="s2">（スピアー）ス… スピー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:19:28.501" end="00:19:30.837" style="s1"><span style="s2">すごい あなた強いのね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:19:30.920" end="00:19:31.921" style="s1"><span style="s2">ネネネ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:19:32.547" end="00:19:33.548" style="s1"><span style="s2">あっ</span></p> 
